{"tid":2159792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對陳雲同班熱狗有疑問","createTime":"2020-08-16T13:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T16:03:46.000Z","uid":31378,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"262ee63cb1a8300e9e907824c932efeefe0a5edb","tid":2159792,"uid":31378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋日日咁屌班醫護屌人戴口罩 佢哋又對抗疫又有咩實質嘅方法呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日都屌話我哋overreaction 又用TB/水痘同武肺比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬呀嗰兩隻係出現左好耐嘅病，而人類亦都透過長時間對依啲病嘅研究得到左足夠嘅認知同埋有疫苗去預防。但係武肺係中共製造嘅生化病毒，人類係仲未研究到任何有效嘅疫苗去預防同治療 。<br />\n所以我完全唔明點解班熱狗可以咁樣相提並論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴口罩只係我哋現階段可以減低感染風險嘅方法 究竟有乜撚嘢問題呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋真係好撚睇唔過眼係度屌醫護話宜家嘅情況係自己攞黎，想知佢哋對抗疫有咩方法可以俾到市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be4b005116eb5750b7c40075d052479b2627298","tid":2159792,"uid":171506,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"陳雲同熱狗寫嘢，主要係畀弱智人士睇"},{"pid":"b52fb7f4b9aed8c490ee3a0eeec1dac65697a778","tid":2159792,"uid":105201,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"你無白卡就唔好嘗試去明白熱普城啲theories啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當笑話睇吓就夠"},{"pid":"93a3a323b8d7a188b8fa1c210f0ca2f775073ea3","tid":2159792,"uid":269061,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"總之網上毓民，現實碌撚。而家乖乖帶taobao 透明口罩"},{"pid":"f1e0cb5734cb760b8af65fa437165076a9fd13e9","tid":2159792,"uid":59641,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"前排先改口話戴口罩